spx.packets.tracks

Class Normal

  • java.lang.Object
    • spx.packets.tracks.Normal

  • public class Normal
extends java.lang.Object
    Normal track reports.

    This class is kept in sync with the C++ SPxPacketTrackNormal structure in "SPxPackets.h".
